These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Food: artichoke, pear
Nationality: brazilian, nigerian
1. Nationality:brazilian is in an even position##4
2. Nationality:nigerian == Food:pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Food   | pear | artichoke |
| Nationality     | nigerian    | brazilian   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
City: hannover, colone
Pet: turtle, snake
1. Pet:turtle is in an odd position##4
2. City:colone is on the left of City:hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| City   | colone | hannover        |
| Pet      | turtle  | snake |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
House: victorian, tower
Transport: quad-bike, airplane
