.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
Transport: train, car
Flower: dahlia, orchid
1. Transport:car is in an odd position##4
2. Flower:dahlia is on the left or right of Transport:train##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Transport   | car | train   |
| Flower         | dahlia | orchid |

